Why Booking.com is the best working place for us?

I think these three key points are most import thing.

1.Safety

Do we need to worry about the manager don't like our question?

Well, No.

We could express ourself in any time, any way, any place.

2.Work Life balance

Do we need to work as 996?

Well, No.

we don't need to worry about dead line and enjoy our every notional holiday.

3.Hope

Does we need to worry about our efforts won't be rewarded?

Well, No.

In booking.com the manager give us hope, the metor give us advice, the peer give us feedback to next step.